sky.engine.util
Class VisitorList<K,L>

java.lang.Object
  sky.engine.util.Visitor<K,L>
      sky.engine.util.VisitorList<K,L>
Type Parameters:
K - - Class type for the keys.
L - - Class type for the links of the keys.
public class VisitorList<K,L>
extends Visitor<K,L>

A data structure for storing a set of keys, each with a set of links; keeping in memory whether those links have been visited to by their parent key.

Since:
24 May 2012. (Last update: 24 May 2012).
Version:
1.0.2.
Author:
Matthew Kelly (Badgerati).

sizeAll

public int[] sizeAll(boolean stacked)

Parameters:
